{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/MalonTitulo.png?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this minimalist strategy game you'll take command of an army fort, tasked with defending it at all costs. To succeed, you'll need to expand your base and train soldiers to stand by your side in defense of the flag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/GifMang2.gif?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/BarraSeparadora.png?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Animals will be a highly valuable resource, enabling you to grow your economy and expand further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/BarraSeparadora.png?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll also have the option to choose the opposing side, establishing your own indigenous settlement and becoming the leader of your people, guiding them in resistance against the <i>huinca</i> invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/Indio.png?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462960/extras/BarraSeparadora.png?t=1737398043\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Both sides feature their own campaign, as well as an infinite survival mode where you can test your skills against endless waves of enem